casebody.data:
MINNESOTA VOTERS ALLIANCE, et al., petitioners,
v.
Joe MANSKY, et al. No. 16-1435. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 13, 2017.

Motion of Cato Institute, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of the American Civil Rights Union, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of Center for Competitive Politics for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit granted.
